---

<div class="mx-4 mt-12 md:mx-12">
  <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-4xl md:text-6xl">Our Team</h2>
  <p class="text-justify text-lg leading-loose md:text-xl md:leading-loose">
    Welcome to 'Our Team' page! We, the students of the A-Level class of
    2021-2023, are thrilled to present you with the result of six months of
    dedicated effort in creating this website. As a passionate team, we took on
    the challenge of designing and developing a platform that reflects the
    essence of our school community. With our collective skills and unwavering
    determination, we meticulously crafted every aspect of this website, from
    coding to visual design, to ensure a seamless and captivating user
    experience. It is our privilege to have been able to contribute our
    technical expertise and creativity to bring this virtual space to life. We
    hope that you find our website informative, engaging, and representative of
    the vibrant spirit of our school.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-8">
    <img class="bg-img hidden lg:block" src="/images/our-team/bg.png" alt="" />
    <div
      class="vertical-center grid grid-cols-1 content-stretch gap-4 py-8 text-center md:grid-cols-4"
    >
      {
        members.map((member) => (
          <MemberCard
            image={member.image}
            name={member.name}
            quote={member.quote}
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 60%;
    z-index: -10;
  }
</style>
